OL,6,FHe said: "While the overall trend in
OL,7,Frecent years is a decrease in the
OL,8,Fnumber of deaths, we're still
OL,9,Fregrettably some way from having none
OL,10,Fin Dumfries and Galloway.
OL,12,F"There is a lot of work taking place
OL,13,Fto address issues and causes related
OL,14,Fto harmful substance use, and there
OL,15,Fcontinues to be an unacceptable level
OL,16,Fand cycle of harm linked to addiction.
