OL,4,Cincrease by 100%
OL,6,F"It's vitally important that we
OL,7,Fcontinue the work to promote means of
OL,8,Fpreventing drug-related deaths,
OL,9,Flooking to treat need during phases of
OL,10,Fillness and suffering, and reducing
OL,11,Fharm."
OL,13,FDespite Scotland continuing to have
OL,14,Fthe worst drug death rate in Europe,
OL,15,Fdata show that deaths from drug misuse
OL,16,Fdropped by 13% - or 155 deaths - in
OL,17,F2024, according to the National
OL,18,FRecords of Scotland (NRS). The decline
OL,19,Ffollows last year's 12% rise that saw
OL,20,Fdeaths climb to 1,172.
