OL,4,Cincrease by 100%
OL,6,FThe most common drugs present were
OL,7,Fopiates and opioids at 80 per cent,
OL,8,Fbenzodiazepines at 56 per cent and
OL,9,Fcocaine at 47 per cent.
OL,11,FMore than nine out of 10 drug misuse
OL,12,Fdeaths were classified as accidental
OL,13,Fpoisonings, with six per cent marked
OL,14,Fas intentional self-poisonings.
OL,16,FIn 2023, Scotland had a rate around
OL,17,Ftwo to three times that of other UK
OL,18,Fcountries for poisoning deaths.
