OL,6,FDeaths involving cocaine remain at
OL,7,Ftheir highest level on record, with
OL,8,F479 deaths for the second year in a
OL,9,Frow.
OL,11,FPhillipa Haxton, head of vital events
OL,12,Fstatistics at the NRS, said: "These
OL,13,Fstatistics show a decrease in drug
OL,14,Fmisuse deaths over the last year and
OL,15,Frepresent the lowest number of deaths
OL,16,Fin the last seven years.
OL,18,F"The longer-term trend shows that drug
OL,19,Fmisuse deaths are still much more
OL,20,Fcommon than they were two decades ago.
