OL,6,F"The statistics also provide
OL,7,Finformation about the people who died
OL,8,Fof a drug misuse death. The figures
OL,9,Fshow us that males continue to be more
OL,10,Fthan twice as likely to have a drug
OL,11,Fmisuse death as females."
